The Dolce&Gabbana Alta Sartoria collection arouses unique emotions as exquisite silks, brocades, velvets, glass and crystals, embroideries and precious fabrics come together in a perfect melody of beauty and Italian craftsmanship.

#DGLovesVenice #DGFattoAMano #MadeInItaly #DolceGabbana

node.text:
Exploring our roots to create what's next: introducing #DGNextChapter, the Women's Fall Winter 21 Fashion Show.
 
In collaboration with @istitutoitalianoditecnologia, the #DGFW21 Collection reveals how technology and craftsmanship, two apparently different worlds, come together in a celebration of Fatto a Mano. The new looks, inspired by robotics research and Artificial Intelligence, also pay tribute to #DolceGabbana DNA of the ‘90s. 
 
Stay tuned for the Fashion Show on Monday, March 1st at 4PM CET.

An unexpected and instinctive Sicily, sublimated by the unique aesthetic vision of @juergentellerstudio for the #DolceGabbana #DGFW21 campaign and enriched by special sounds, conceived and composed by the photographer himself from his own experience on the set. 
  
Ettore, the Ragusano donkey featured in the campaign, was cared for and protected for the duration of the shoot under the supervision of a qualified veterinarian, who monitored its health during transport and while on-set. 
  
Hollywood® is the trademark and intellectual property of Hollywood Chamber of Commerce. All Rights Reserved. 
  
Discover the collection at the link in bio.

For this year’s @metmuseum Gala “In America: A Lexicon of Fashion”, #DolceGabbana partnered with gender fluid designer @harris_reed and @metcostumeinstitute to create a custom gown for @the_real_iman composed of a back-tied jacquard bustier with rich silk ribbons, paired with Reed’s signature H Flare trousers, all embellished with hand painted and applied feathers, crafted from Italian brocade and emphasized by a crinoline skirt. To complete the look, a structured headpiece made of white feathers and embellished with golden applications. 

Directed by @bardiazeinali
Director of Photography @packdrawn
Executive Producers @oliviamweiss @steeveeeeee
Motion Producer @ianmilan_
Production Company @prodn_artandcommerce
Steadicam @yoshisteadiop
Movement @luisa_opalesky
Edit & Post Production @modern.post
Set Design @davidjameswhite_
Creative Music Production @searchpartymusic @premiermusicgroup @winslowbright
Met Production Manager @beckyschear

#DGCelebs #MetGala2021 #MetInAmerica #DGEditorials
